casebody.data:
Tuesday, September 14, 1999

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

99-1110. State ex rel. Murray v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 98AP-773. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. It appears from the records of this court that appellant has not filed a merit brief, due September 7, 1999, in compliance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court *1482and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed sua sponte.
